e mixture evenly between 4 bowls.\",\"5\":\"Enjoy!\"}','{\"fat\":8,\"calories\":199,\"sugar\":1,\"carbohydrates\":4,\"fiber\":1,\"protein\":25}','','4','\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/09765c685bc8428d81b4093438e87ed2/BFV13225_ShrimpStir-Fry4Ways-FB1080SQ.jpg\"','2 tablespoons sesame oil||1 pound large shrimp, peeled and deveined||½ teaspoon salt, divided||2 cups mushrooms, sliced||1 cup asparagus, sliced||1 tablespoon ginger, minced||1 tablespoon low-sodium soy sauce||','stove_top||chinese||seafood||dinner||weeknight||pan_fry||easy||healthy||date_night||tongs||saute_pan||mixing_bowl||wooden_spoon||measuring_spoons||dry_measuring_cups||pyrex||chefs_knife||cutting_board||light_bites||low_carb||low_calorie||high_protein||low_sugar||dairy_free||pescatarian||keto'),('da-5869233d4c63','\"Pizza In A Mug\"','{\"0\":\"Add the biscuit to a microwave-safe mug. MIcrowave for 30 seconds, until the biscuit starts to puff up.\",\"1\":\"In a small bowl, mix together the marinara sauce, garlic powder, and a pinch of basil.\",\"2\":\"Spoon the sauce over the par-cooked biscuit, then top with the mozzarella and mini pepperoni.\",\"3\":\"Loosely cover the mug with a paper towel and microwave for 30–45 seconds more, until the cheese is melted and the biscuit is cooked through.\",\"4\":\"Top with another pinch of basil, then let the mini pizza cool for about 5 minutes before serving.\",\"5\":\"Enjoy!\"}','{\"protein\":44,\"fat\":72,\"calories\":1746,\"sugar\":39,\"carbohydrates\":238,\"fiber\":12}','\"Need pizza in a flash? Stuck in a dorm room with just a microwave? Feeling lazy? We have the perfect 60-second pizza recipe that tastes almost like the real thing. The secret? Canned biscuits!\"','1','\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/94293849eb0949bfa7c6c88510ed32db/BFV71390_6WaysToCookCannedBiscuitsWithoutFollowingThePackageInstructions_MJC_YT_FINAL.jpg\"','1 unbaked canned biscuit||2 tablespoons marinara sauce||Pinch of garlic powder||2 pinches 