alt, pepper, dried basil, dried oregano, and dried parsley. Cook until the onions are caramelized and soft. About 10 minutes.\",\"3\":\"Add the tomato paste and cook until the tomato paste darkens slightly.\",\"4\":\"Add in the diced tomatoes and the sausage slices into the pan, stir, and let the sauce come to a simmer.\",\"5\":\"Add in half the grated parmesan, spinach, the cooked pasta, and stir to combine.\",\"6\":\"Spoon in fresh dollaps of the ricotta cheese, garnish with fresh basil, more grated parmesan, and serve!\",\"7\":\"Enjoy!\"}','{\"protein\":30,\"fat\":33,\"calories\":587,\"sugar\":10,\"carbohydrates\":47,\"fiber\":4}','','6','\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/d1d185b20fdd4e9181169d0115d348de/FinalFBforpkg.jpg\"','1 tablespoon olive oil,||5 hot Italian sausage links||1 large yellow onion, chopped||5 garlic cloves, minced||Salt, to taste||Pepper, to taste||1 tablespoon dried oregano||1 tablespoon dried basil||1 tablespoon dried parsley||12 ounces tomato paste||15 ounces diced tomatoes||2 cups grated parmesan, divided||2 cups spinach||1 pound cooked rigatonis||1 cup ricotta cheese||Basil to garnish.||','comfort_food||easy||weeknight||dinner||one_pot_or_pan||stove_top||sauce_pan||dutch_oven||tongs||pyrex||cheese_grater||spatula||chefs_knife||cutting_board||dry_measuring_cups||liquid_measuring_cup||measuring_spoons||epoca_walmart||high_protein||high_fiber'),('db-f45245eb3536','\"Beetroot \\u0026 Feta Burgers\"','{\"0\":\"To a large bowl, add the beetroot, sweet potato, salt, black pepper, garlic granules, smoked paprika, lemon zest, coriander, tahini, feta, eggs, and breadcrumbs. Mix until thoroughly combined. You should achieve a wet, sticky mixture that should just about come together when formed into a burger.\",\"1\":\"Next place a large frying pan over a low-medium heat and add around 1 cm (½ in) of oil. You need enough oil so the burgers are at least halfway covered with the oil when they are in the pan.\",\"2\":\"Once the oil is